{
  "stem": "4247.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was not part of the-- of the board of directors of the-- of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I have no direct recollection of his behavior-- Friedman Denes's behavior.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my general impression of that time was that while, you know, the, the sermon he delivered was impeccable and, at times, very moving, but he lacked in leadership action, right, which would have-- which would have [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] enthused them-- the, the, the Jewish people there to, to do certain things or not to do certain things, to go away.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was not a-- he was not a, a leader in this sense.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, in fact, it was no leader in this sense because there were no such personalities and mainly because the circumstances were not, not-- have not been allowing for such personalities to develop.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm coming back to, when you were in a straitjacket, then you just sit there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's nothing you can do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you are gagged, what, what do you do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just sit there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were wearing of the Jewish stars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they started to-- they started again, a very well-proven method of the past, what they used in other areas-- to concentrate us in, in confined areas.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I was called up on the 15th of May, 1944-- being a 19-year-old or 19-and-1/2-year-old Jewish boy-- into a-- into a, a, a labor camp, which was the alternative of, of military duties for a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, we know that we will be called up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we had not been Jewish, we would have been called up, in any case, in the military service.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So why should the Jewish boys be, be spared?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
